Enter (or exit) a Spectral State. In this state, you:
Resist bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage from non-magical, non-silvered attacks;
Can move through solid objects and creatures as if difficult terrain (if you end your turn in one, you are shunted to the nearest unoccupied space and take 1d10 force damage per 5 ft. traveled);
Gain a flying speed equal to your walking speed, and the ability to hover.
